adept.common

Class DocumentEventArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.Item
      • adept.common.HltContent
        • adept.common.DocumentEventArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasScoredUnaryAttributes, Serializable

    public class DocumentEventArgument
extends HltContent
implements HasScoredUnaryAttributes, Serializable
    Represents the argument of an event. Unlike EventMentionArgument, this represents the participation of an entity in an event rather than an extent of text, though supporting provenances may be made optionally available.

    For high-level documentation of all event classes, see DocumentEvent.

    This class is locally immutable.
